{"tid":766035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那外交部稱中國真誠幫湄公河下游國　指美國官員別有用心","createTime":"2018-08-03T09:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T10:03:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a1f5b9af11a34f71a47f1fa7067b1469143a94","tid":766035,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那你個仆街仔，你上游狂起水壩，下游用屎水呀?</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410484-20180803.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410484-20180803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=2cbd8d77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1410484-20180803.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a2f9dc10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1410484-20180803.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，中國真誠幫助湄公河下游國家，得到高度評價。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽回應有美國國務院官員指出，中國在位於國內的湄公河上游修築堤壩，對下游國家產生不利影響。耿爽說，美方官員的言論毫無根據，別有用心。<br />\n<br />\n他強調中方一直十分重視湄公河下游國家的關注及需求，彼此保持密切溝通，中方致力與相關國家，分享有關水資源的資訊，在防洪及抗旱等方面開展合作。"},{"pid":"32e758c5bee2237c7472cfc978ca774a6532852d","tid":766035,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"要不是中國照。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"067c62342a17cc411bcdd40a286184895233e397","tid":766035,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"中國得閒咪深夜洩洪<br />\n<br />\n搞到下游國家水災死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae16560f9c9203576226e184c54eed22b692292","tid":766035,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"p