ink target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20160725/37322019</a>"},{"pid":"9acbb1035715909b3a56080b835df9e29742b2d6","tid":766035,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab1017be5beba819d35d46119f109ce909f9b36","tid":766035,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:57:58.000Z","msg":"起完水壩，咪可以再叫下游國家俾錢起輸水管，然後收錢賣水。<br />\n<br />\n將東江水模式用喺呢度。<br />\n<br />\n當年東江水香港仲要先俾錢等佢有錢做基建輸水。"},{"pid":"2d232ac66d0eb25fa8ecb0a3b9faecbad2e48784","tid":766035,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8ae16560f9c9203576226e184c54eed22b692292","tid":766035,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"067c62342a17cc411bcdd40a286184895233e397","tid":766035,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"中國得閒咪深夜洩洪<br />\n<br />\n搞到下游國家水災死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"一招斃命印度？外媒：水壩是中國的大規模毀滅武器<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2177575\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2177575&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=ac4f516c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2177575&h=87a4ac24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2177575</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">中國為何瘋狂修建水壩？控制「亞洲水塔」等同巨大權力</span><br />\n據美媒《國家利益》報導，湄公河、恆河、長江、印度河等重要河川都是自西藏高原發源，由「亞洲水塔」之稱的喜馬拉雅山的雪水而來。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">稱一擊必殺？印度學者：中國可利用水壩輕鬆針對印度</span><br />\n據《印度教徒報（The Hindu）》19日報導，印度外交部抗議中國未遵守協議，在汛期與印度分享「布拉馬普特拉河（Brahmaputra River）」和「薩特萊傑河（Satluj River）」的水文數據，而印度必須使用這些數據以發出準確的洪水警報。另外，過去印度也痛批中國水霸無預警洩洪，造成東北地區5萬人無家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">洩洪沒通知 河北遭滅村</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20160725/37322019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20160725%2F37322019&d=o01ryfUGnJETu8mWdWEnCbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=a91c3017\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2F20160725%2F37322019&h=6ecdcec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/daily/20160725/37322019</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}